## Component Specs

### Buttons
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: #F97316;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
}
```

### Cards
```css
.card {
  background: #F0FDFA;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
```

## Anti-Patterns (禁止事項)
- Emojis as icons → Use Lucide SVG
- Missing cursor:pointer on clickables
- Instant state changes → Use transitions (150-300ms)
- Low contrast text → 4.5:1 minimum
- Invisible focus states

## Pre-Delivery Checklist
- [ ] All icons from Lucide
- [ ] cursor-pointer on clickables
- [ ] Hover states with transitions
- [ ] Focus states visible
- [ ] Responsive: 375px, 768px, 1024px
